div.p:
He then listed four short term priorities in this order: more Belgian officers;
                    Israeli training of two battalions; retention of Nigerian troops after June 30;
                    and US supply of air capability. I pointed out Nigerians would require
                    burden-sharing and mentioned that Adoula
                    suggested Tunisians as another possible source. He commented Tunisians would be
                    “second best.”
